snippet.title: Import Tuner Challenge [XB360][60fps] - Gameplay & CUSTOMIZATION
snippet.description: Here's some Gameplay from Import Tuner Challenge, aka Tokyo Xtreme Racer. This is a Xbox Exclusive Release and is not available for other consoles. Enjoy these 30 minutes gameplay featuring a few races and a full depth of customization.
